rows.label: qev040404_MSG0001
rows.name:
Satsuuu! Come back hooome!
Gotsu sad from missing you![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev040404_SEL0011
rows.name: Tell Gotsu that Satsu has been found.

rows.label: qev040404_SEL0021
rows.name: Tell Gotsu that Satsu is in heaven now.

rows.label: qev040404_MSG0002
rows.name: Oh, whew! Now Gotsu can go back home.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev040404_MSG0003
rows.name: Missing everyone was starting to drive Gotsu crazy.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev040404_MSG0004
rows.name: Gotsu see friend back at caravan![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev040404_MSG0005
rows.name: No! Heart of Gotsu feel like shattering...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev040404_MSG0006
rows.name: Gotsu never see Satsu again! Sad! So sad![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev040404_MSG0007
rows.name: ...Meh? Friend was teasing? Satsu is back at caravan?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev040404_MSG0008
rows.name:
Friend is monster! But Gotsu happy Satsu is alive,
so Gotsu forgive terrible trick.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev040404_MSG0009
rows.name: Gotsu eager to get back and see everyone![ST:wait ]
